Package: r4sub
Title: Easily Install and Load the R4SUB Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", , "prm@outlook.in", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'r4sub' package is a meta-package that installs and loads
    core packages of the R4SUB clinical submission readiness ecosystem.
    Loading 'r4sub' attaches 'r4subcore', 'r4subtrace', 'r4subscore',
    'r4subrisk', 'r4subdata', and 'r4subprofile'. The dashboard package
    'r4subui' is available but not auto-attached.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4sub
BugReports: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4sub/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2),
    r4subcore,
    r4subdata,
    r4subprofile,
    r4subrisk,
    r4subscore,
    r4subtrace
Imports:
    cli,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    utils
Suggests:
    r4subui,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
